(8x+4)(\sqrt{4x+1})
\frac{2}{\sqrt{4x+1}}(2x+1)^2
(2x+1)^2 \sqrt{4x+1}
\begin{aligned} &(8x+4)(\sqrt{4x+1})+\frac{2}{\sqrt{4x+1}}(2x+1)^2 \\ =& \frac{(8x+4)(4x+1)}{\sqrt{4x+1}}+\frac{2(2x+1)^2}{\sqrt{4x+1}} \\ =& \frac{32x^2 + 24x + 4}{\sqrt{4x+1}} + \frac{8x^2 + 8x + 2}{\sqrt{4x+1}} \\ =& \frac{40x^2 + 32x + 6}{\sqrt{4x+1}} \\ =& \frac{2(10x + 3)(2x+1)}{\sqrt{4x+1}}. \end{aligned}
